{
  "texts": [
    "The boy's desire is for the girl to believe him.",
    "The boy is desirous of the girl believing him.",
    "are parsed to a unique AMR.",
    "2 In this AMR, 'desire-01' has the suffix '-01' representing the specific sense of the verb 'desire' based on PropBank; want, crave, desire.",
    "The ARG0 connects the verb 'desire' to its subject, 'boy', and ARG1 connects this verb to 'believe', its proposition."
